name: Goose a Gone
description:
You, a young goose, decide to annoy your human neighbors with some honking. As you continually annoy them, you may find they are harder to stop then you thought before! Get the highest score you can before your neighbors kick you off the street and back into the river. Good luck!

Special Thanks to FMA Artists Scott Holmes and Checkie Brown for their work.
